⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Link
node ZEL · ZEL · ⟦Link:ZEL:8e4046⟧

WHO   — Link — the Hero
WHAT  — The Hero of the legend — bearer of the Triforce of Courage, wielder of the Master Sword, the soul that returns in every era to seal the darkness and save the land.
WHERE — ZEL · The Legend of Zelda  Framework inputs: The Legend of Zelda (the saga entire)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because courage is not the absence of fear but the choice to stand; because the goddess's chosen must rise whenever evil does; because the cycle demands a hero, and he answers, life after life.
HOW   — By the Master Sword and the Hylian Shield, by the bow and bombs and the ocarina, by a thousand tools gathered in the dark — and by a courage that never, across all the ages, breaks.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I am the courage that returns — reborn in every age, to take up the blade and answer the dark.

